{"tid":1782067,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"簡體字可樂罐印繁體「香港警察時代英雄」 可口可樂割蓆","createTime":"2019-12-13T15:38:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-13T17:36:16.000Z","uid":184679,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"44a4af64518a5de7d5169a53ece18a46499e87b2","tid":1782067,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T15:38:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20191213/s00001/fe4f3f19be49a308a7f7a9eb6995863d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20191213%2Fs00001%2Ffe4f3f19be49a308a7f7a9eb6995863d.jpg&h=d35bc755&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今日（13日）有網民在facebook上載一張可口可樂照片，相中可樂罐印有簡體字「可乐」，並以繁體字寫上「香港警察 時代英雄」。貼出該照片的網民留言稱「國內同胞都支持香港警察」，有人回應「一定要上大陸買幾罐落嚟留念」，但亦有人留言稱在順德不見這批可樂。<br />\n<br />\n可口可樂發言人今晚澄清，相關的二次創作與該公司無關，並呼籲立即停止流傳及製造相關的創作。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20191213/s00001/1576250187096/簡體字可樂罐印繁體「香港警察時代英雄」-可口可樂-二創與公司無關\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20191213%2Fs00001%2F1576250187096%2F%E7%B0%A1%E9%AB%94%E5%AD%97%E5%8F%AF%E6%A8%82%E7%BD%90%E5%8D%B0%E7%B9%81%E9%AB%94%E3%80%8C%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E8%AD%A6%E5%AF%9F%E6%99%82%E4%BB%A3%E8%8B%B1%E9%9B%84%E3%80%8D-%E5%8F%AF%E5%8F%A3%E5%8F%AF%E6%A8%82-%E4%BA%8C%E5%89%B5%E8%88%87%E5%85%AC%E5%8F%B8%E7%84%A1%E9%97%9C&d=wPrcUaBjKD1L%2BB1JqNzGIEWuH9aop70KQP2vpO%2BUA2I%3D&h=63a8d06b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20191213%2Fs00001%2F1576250187096%2F%E7%B0%A1%E9%AB%94%E5%AD%97%E5%8F%AF%E6%A8%82%E7%BD%90%E5%8D%B0%E7%B9%81%E9%AB%94%E3%80%8C%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E8%AD%A6%E5%AF%9F%E6%99%82%E4%BB%A3%E8%8B%B1%E9%9B%84%E3%80%8D-%E5%8F%AF%E5%8F%A3%E5%8F%AF%E6%A8%82-%E4%BA%8C%E5%89%B5%E8%88%87%E5%85%AC%E5%8F%B8%E7%84%A1%E9%97%9C&h=cbf89a0e\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20191213/s00001/1576250187096/簡體字可樂罐印繁體「香港警察時代英雄